      "title": "Gotabaya Rajapaksa arrives in Singapore",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President Gotabaya Rajapaksa who flew into Singapore from the Maldives on Thursday (July 14) evening, arrived on board a Saudia Airlines flight which touched down at Changi airport at 7.17pm, local time.",
        "Rajapaksa is however expected to be in Singapore only on transit and is expected to fly into the Middle East later in the day. (JH)"
      ],
